Feature: Access log in options
As a user
I want to be able to enter my log in credentials
So that I can log in to the app

@login
Scenario: Accessing login page
Given I am on the home page
When I click on "log in"
And I am not logged in
Then I should see username and password fields

=============================================================

Feature: App login
As a user
I want to be able to log in to the app with valid credentials
So that I can view my personal app data

@login
Scenario: Logging into app
Given I am on login page
When I enter valid credentials into username and password fields
And I click "login"
Then I should see my personal homepage

=============================================================

Feature: App location
As a user
I want to be able to locate my current position on the map
So that I can begin exercises in the vicinity

@location
Scenario: Viewing current location
Given I am on the home page
When I click "Start"
Then I should see a marker on a map showing current location

=============================================================

Feature: Personal statistics
As a user
I want to be able to track my scores and times to view later
So that I can check my progress

@tracking
Scenario: Viewing personal scores
Given I am on the home page
When I click "Tracking"
Then I should see a list of previous times and scores for exercises
